<br />
i may add one thing to this guide of pulling hard ldon; i learned from an experienced bard (thanks deryen) how to efficiently pull in Ruk (EC ldon); instead of using harmony ( debuff) to pull, i use Druzzil (dispell). it has sensibly the same range, but has the advantage of debuffing their d*mn buffs and mostly their sow; i used to avoid EC hard as i was dying at least 2-3 times everytime. With this i can actually run to group without being smack down by a freight train. 
<br />

<br />
as for paci, i find ruk again to be the hardest, even with a cha buff getting me to 255, i still get most of time a resist and aggro; to reduce the chance of aggroing on a failed paci, i have to pulse cha song before.
