				<td colspan="2"><span>Some advice on Cha ............. I am going to make a bard when I get home (had one then deleted him and wish I had not).  Currently I have a 65 chanter and have made it a point to keep my Cha maxed at all times.  There is a lot of debate about the effects of Cha and this is what I have found.  Cha will effect resist on charm and mez and how long charm last.  When it comes to paci it will effect if you get agro.  I love pulling and pull all the time.  IMO chanters are the 2nd best pullers in the game (bards being first,  I have a 65 monk and still think chanters are better at pulling then monks).  I pull hard ldon's all the time and very rarely do I get bad pulls due to resist (mostly it is from not seeing a mob before I pull).</span></td>
